//
// Advanced time series forecasting models including:
// - SARIMA (Seasonal ARIMA)
// - VAR (Vector Autoregression)
// - VARMAX (VAR with exogenous variables)
// - State Space Models
// - Theta Method
// - TBATS (Trigonometric Box-Cox ARMA Trend Seasonal)
// - Prophet-style decomposition
// - Croston's method for intermittent demand
// - ETS (Error, Trend, Seasonal) framework
//
